metadata.name: Soul Sessions 1
metadata.description:
The intention behind my new podcast 'Soul Sessions' presented by Huddln Radio is to dive into deeper conversations with members of the web3 community who I respect and admire. Under the tweets on the timeline, under the latest project to be minted - what currents are running through their lives? What rhythms is their soul moving to at this time?

This piece co-created with Midjourney AI is my visual interpretation of what is happening during these conversations on that plane that is outside of, within and throughout the dimension that holds the frequency of our physical existence.

People who mint this piece will be welcomed into my growing collector community as the first collectors of my visual art! So for that alone, I thank you and am honoured that you would join me on this new journey.

I would also like to thank my dear friend Jonny October for being the instigator and inspiration for me to begin to explore this exciting new creative medium.
